1:20:41.749 --> 1:20:44.317
-It's where I wanna work.
-Yeah.

1:20:45.318 --> 1:20:46.406
Whoa, Blake.

1:20:50.323 --> 1:20:52.412
-This is so cool.
-So awesome.

1:20:52.586 --> 1:20:54.110
Definitely us.

